 Details Overview How to add existing proxy file .PAC into Geocortex?
Solution This can be done using the web.configs of the REST and Manager applications(C:\Program Files (x86)\Latitude Geographics\Geocortex Essentials\Default\REST Elements\Manager\web.config) by using the following in the system.net section as below.
&lt;system.net&gt; &lt;defaultProxy useDefaultCredentials=&quot;true&quot;&gt; &lt;proxy usesystemdefault=&quot;False&quot; scriptLocation=&quot;http://pacproxy.com.au/proxy.pac&quot; /&gt; &lt;/defaultProxy&gt;
